      <title>七国集团声明草案警告中东局势“难以控制”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/draft-g-7-statement-warns-of-uncontrollable-mideast-escalation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博新闻看到的一份声明草案显示，七国集团将警告称，危险的袭击循环“有可能加剧中东地区无法控制的升级”，并将谴责伊朗最近对以色列发动的导弹袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/draft-g-7-statement-warns-of-uncontrollable-mideast-escalation</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 18:44:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
