    <item>
      <title>摩尔多瓦称俄罗斯投入巨资阻挠其加入欧盟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/moldova-says-russia-channeling-millions-to-thwart-its-eu-path</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩尔多瓦当局称，他们发现了一项由俄罗斯支持的行动，涉及 13 万名摩尔多瓦公民，旨在影响本月对总统玛雅·桑杜的欧洲愿望至关重要的投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/moldova-says-russia-channeling-millions-to-thwart-its-eu-path</guid>
